content.html: BREAKING: Twitter has dissolved its Trust & Safety Council in its entirety, per a new internal email. The Council focused on Online Safety and Harassment, Human and Digital Rights, Suicide Prevention and Mental Health, Child Sexual Exploitation, and Dehumanization on Twitter.
content.value:
BREAKING: Twitter has dissolved its Trust & Safety Council in its entirety, per a new internal email.

The Council focused on Online Safety and Harassment, Human and Digital Rights, Suicide Prevention and Mental Health, Child Sexual Exploitation, and Dehumanization on Twitter.
